title: Shall we open the Telegram group chat to token holders, or move over to syndicate?
body: Team Culture is growing. Should we let the new folks in that have successfully passed the stack of tokens on? Or shall we move to Syndicate fully? Other options?
choices: Wait for Rug Pull's Got Talent to begin
